item.title: Build QuantumPT
item.description: This page shows you how to build QuantumPT application from scratch on Windows 7 using pyqtdeploy. Requirements ALL packages need to be installed for 32-bits, it will work even if you have a 64-bits system. Windows 7 (x64 or x86) Python 3.6.x (any version should do it, e.g 3.6.1) Qt 5.8.0 for Windows 32-bit (VS 2015, 1.0 GB) Microsoft Visual Studio 2015 Community Edition sip 4.19.2 (source) PyQt 5.
